reasoning, and you're more

00:05:39.680 --> 00:05:41.660 align:middle line:84%
understanding that it
takes serving people

00:05:41.660 --> 00:05:43.370 align:middle line:84%
to have a source of
income, and it takes

00:05:43.370 --> 00:05:45.260 align:middle line:90%
