value on consumerism.

00:06:47.092 --> 00:06:49.300 align:middle line:84%
They want the fancy lifestyle
of the rich and famous.

00:06:49.300 --> 00:06:51.190 align:middle line:84%
>> So they can have
a value on themself?

00:06:51.190 --> 00:06:51.990 align:middle line:90%
>> Yeah.

00:06:51.990 --> 00:06:53.330 align:middle line:90%
>> But just not a value on--

00:06:53.330 --> 00:06:55.580 align:middle line:84%
>> Well, they won't have
