00:07:01.160 --> 00:07:02.420 align:middle line:90%
So you've got a choice.

00:07:02.420 --> 00:07:04.220 align:middle line:84%
Either set goals that
match your values

00:07:04.220 --> 00:07:06.590 align:middle line:84%
